document: Hi, I'm trki omar, a new graduated engineer and an angular django developer, since preparatory school of engineering i was fascinated by computer science and mathematics so i learned python and the fundamentals of mathematics then i got 376 as rank in the preparatory national exam so i got ENIS as a school of engineering where i studied a lot of technologies such as Java, spring boot, JEE also PHP, symfony and Python, Django and flask and Js, Angular and react. I got my experience from internships i had, my end-of-training internship was about a platform for TDHD and i using django and angular as frameworks to realize the project. i got my diploma engineer in computer science and mathematics from ENIS and now I'm looking for new opportunities to start my career as full stack developer inside the company.
